name: Chojo Island
description:
Chojo (The Top) Floating Island is an island that located above the skies, No one knows to where it float and who might live on the top of the broken ruin. Many believes that everytime the rain started, the water that fall to the earth is the water from Chojo's waterfall.

This drawing was made recently with my very minimum experience making pixel art, I hope this art brings you smile as it gave me when the first time i saw it float.
